Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hong Kong — 1994
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei, save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Mei Ling!\NIt's just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Hong Kong,\Nto FREEDOM... Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast Invasion\Nepisode 5\NHong Kong Resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the green rain which\Nmoved into the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hong Kong-Macao area\Nfrom southern China...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...continues to mystify\Nthe people living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One morning after the incident,\Nthe strangely colored rain had...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...vanished with no lasting\Neffect on anyone caught in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Authorities continue to\Nlook for some explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, that high pressure\Nfront off the continent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should be giving Japan\Nclear weather for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. Why so glum\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.\NThis scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you attacked\Nsome girl and she fought back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe I'm looking for\Nsomeone different for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You mean you did?!\NYou tried to rape someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy who serves a religion\Nand does that goes to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your temple's been breaking\Nthose rules for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! What if one of the\Ntemple families heard that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one\Nwho's supposed to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't try to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why the scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was demonstrating\Nsome kempo for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that like karate?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Ungyosai\Nmonks have been passing down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chinese Hokuba kempo for\Nthe last 4,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad just suddenly decided it\Nwas time to pass it on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, I hate the thought of\Nspending the holidays training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could find some\Nexcuse to get out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong?\N- It's nothing, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.\NI just need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no trouble, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Muneto.\NJust go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...\NYou know, a girl thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. I'll be fine if I\Njust rest a little in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take too long\Nor I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?\NAt a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Give it to me!\NGive me your warm wetness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fingers...\NCan't control myself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Demon Beast\Nwas finally dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget the feel\Nof my rough tongue over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you\Nto see me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it.\NDon't remember! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chuan Zui Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chuan Zui Ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient Chinese\Nname for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hidden intuition\Nof the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doorway to the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep behind the door\Nto her memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kayo fears the\NDemon Beast's resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the memories Kayo\Nstill carries of the Demon Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid they\Nmay be unconsciously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...opening the door\Nto her Chuan Zui Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's body isn't like\Nthat of normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is doomed to attract\Nthe Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her feelings as the Beast's\Nmother are at war...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the good side\Nof her human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I really don't understand\Nwhat you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stand it that\Nwe thought the Demon Beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was gone for good, but now\Nits memory will keep on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...coming back to haunt\Nus in Kayo's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must redirect the power\Nof her Chuan Zui Ji properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and Kayo will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And how do I do that?!\N- That I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exists deep\Nwithin the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Maitreya can't\Nhelp with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, wait!\NYou damned fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you\Ndegenerate monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Demon Beast\Ninfluencing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, too,\Nis cursed greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namu Amida Butsu...\NNamu Amida Butsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get a good shot!\N- Her? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with you?\NCome on, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come on!\NSnap it! Snap it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong?\N- Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best place to play\Nhard and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But roller coasters go too fast.\NI can't stand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we\Nride one by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best place I know to have some\Nreal fun without anyone knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, pal! I'm definitely\Nnot in the mood today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's the best way to\Nforget about everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I don't think\NI can stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't think girls\Nare like guys that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kayo, you do...?\N- Yes, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we wait till the time's\Nright, it'll be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that would be a\Nbetter place to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you...?! Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you wanted to\Ndo it in the temple of Kannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame! Shame, Muneto!\NYou'll go to hell for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must run in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of THAT talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tickets! Ticketsl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! You're Akaori\NLand's one millionth customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win a trip for two\Nto Hong Kong and Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No lies.\NHere's your proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are gonna have one\Nhell of a holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But I don't have a passport...\N- It won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you! Good for you!\NCongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guardian spirit Tairunto\Nis growing well in Saijan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 800-year wish of the\NTriads is about to be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful to help\NTairunto to be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do we have\NTairunto's mother yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have her, all right.\NWe're preparing to bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we needn't worry about\Nallowing the heaven-sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dragon children\Nto grow to maturity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to protect\NTairunto at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. Tairunto's resurrection\Nis our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tairunto's\Npersonal guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bandits on the river and\NTriad troops defend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until his rebirth, no one\Nmust know about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we cut off the\Nbusiness talk for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...evening and get\Nto the entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the everlasting\Nprosperity of the Triads!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is G7. As I suspected,\Nthe Demon Beast has begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...its resurrection in\Nthe Hong Kong-Macao area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hong Kong gangster Triads\Nare already its carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a termination team in here.\NI'll look for the main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're luring her to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're going after Kayo,\Nthey'll also go after...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's so pretty!\NMuneto, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing this really\Ngets me in the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some REAL\Nfun tonight, huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't you ever\Nthink about anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun feeling like we're\Ngoing someplace exotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're feeling better now,\Naren't you, Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relaxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. I just came\Nto deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a pass from the\NTaipans in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy what you're\Nsmuggling. The drugs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me! I won't be paying\Nin Hong Kong dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking U.S. greenbacks.\NGold ingots, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you really after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you pirates have some\Nreal bad asses with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hire the\NKhmer Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kill a woman\Nleading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Taipans in Hong Kong will\Npay double for what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you after?\N- I can't say. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you once I confirm\Nmy target. Nothing till then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so damn funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you want to\Nkill... Is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Demon Beast has\Ncontrol of them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, now I've lost Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My luck sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...\NI'll meet you in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay together, the\Nriver bandits will get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead them off,\Nand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think\Nwe crossed the border?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you stay alive, I can\Ngive you the future I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to my uncle's junk\Nin Aberdeen Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes\Nto get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are? Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hide in this fog, you\Ncan make it to the river's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei, don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H..Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if can't escape to Hong Kong,\NI wanna be with you, hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you illegal immigrants?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a tourist.\NI have my Japanese passport here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now quit spoiling the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it too much and it'll\Nstart to hurt, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay out here,\Nshe really will get arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. You're awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. Relax. You had a\Nfever, but it's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need some food.\NOh, and medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll\Nneed a doctor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can leave the\Ncomplicated part for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel front doesn't seem\Nto mind you're an illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Muneto.\NWhat's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it. Anyway, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a dress for you, too.\NNothing fancy, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to meet someone.\NWait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a few things to take\Ncare of. Bye, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. I was worried when\NI found you weren't back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to go out\Nlooking for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd probably\Nbe waiting for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in. Hong Kong's gotta\Nbe the sweatiest place on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want to get\Nin the shower fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So would I. With you.\N- Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish we had an air\Nconditioner in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think they'd book a better\Nhotel for their millionth customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I like these places\Nbetter than the fancy hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. This is way more\Nexotic than a luxury hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I like to go out for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?!\NKayo's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, er, uh... Just checking\Nfor an emergency exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In case there was a fire or\Nan earthquake or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:23:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks okay. If anything happens,\Nwe can make it to the fire escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I bought it\Ncheap at a little stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even the one\NI liked best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a little low cut.\NBut it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No teasing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you're the only\Nguy for me, tonight I'm yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we came to Hong Kong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't go peeping\Nat the room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... You saw I\Nwas sorta curious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to\Nbe curious about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:23:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, gehtly.\NNo need to rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.92,0:25:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.34,0:25:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.35,0:25:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.60,0:25:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.98,0:25:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.65,0:25:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Came looking for you and\Npicked up this Beast larva.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.62,0:25:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.99,0:25:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interplanetary Mutual Observation\Nagent. Code name: G7.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.54,0:25:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's an I MO\Nagent doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast.\NThis girl was infested.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.34,0:26:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.59,0:26:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. These things\Naren't very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they can control any\Nman or woman they get into!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.60,0:26:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.73,0:26:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, if you're an agent, then\Nyou know what this leads to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.15,0:26:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precursor to the\NDemon Beast's resurrection?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.16,0:26:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The green rain fell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.16,0:26:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I heard\Nabout it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.50,0:26:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast's spirit\Nfell along with the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.17,0:26:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.79,0:26:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken control of the\Nriver bandits and the Triads.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.67,0:26:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're working to bring their\Nnew king completely back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.14,0:26:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's being reborn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.81,0:26:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan is sealed off to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.89,0:26:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's trying to succeed here\Nwhere it failed before!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.56,0:27:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside. She may be\Ninnocent, but if I let her go...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.81,0:27:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she may give birth to\Ntwo or three more!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.82,0:27:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I won't let you!\N- Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.53,0:27:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling can't die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.74,0:27:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone she loves\Nthat she has to see first!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Muneto!\N- It's not your decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.20,0:27:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you barbecued everyone\Nwho's carried a Demon Beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.21,0:27:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd have\Nto kill Kayo, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'll have to\Ntake care of her, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.92,0:27:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before the Beast\Ncan get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.88,0:27:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you will!\NYou son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.89,0:27:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your own mistake to let\Nit lure you out of the sealed zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.47,0:27:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lure me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.31,0:27:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it?!\NIdiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.60,0:27:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that millionth\Ncustomer thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.61,0:27:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All a plan carried out\Nby the Beast's minions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.32,0:27:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.99,0:27:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.99,0:27:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.01,0:28:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, the Flame Buster!\NToast these fuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.03,0:28:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.71,0:28:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kayo!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.05,0:28:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.06,0:28:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:29:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up. Didn't think those\Nbandits would come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.73,0:29:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kayo?!\NWhere are they taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.73,0:29:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up the river. I've been picking\Nup an incredibly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.74,0:29:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Demon Beast life reading deep in\Nthe jungles up the main tributary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.74,0:29:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Demon Beast king.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What if it manages\Nto join with Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.04,0:29:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Demon Beast\Nwill definitely be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.41,0:29:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling, who was that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.42,0:29:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes, his face...\NThey seemed different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.76,0:29:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he reacted to my voice.\NIt had to have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.76,0:29:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been my Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.10,0:29:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already been taken\Nover by the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.39,0:29:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.10,0:29:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He doesn't have any memories\Nor even his human soul anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, G7!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.78,0:29:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's the truth!\N- I said cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.07,0:30:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this.\NLet's get ourselves upriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.30,0:30:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boat's sensors are\Nset to Demon Beast readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.47,0:30:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put this\Non your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.76,0:30:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...make sure you kill\Nthe king Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.81,0:30:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you'll burn\Nright along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.43,0:30:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.94,0:30:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real problem is getting\Nto that thing in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.53,0:30:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The river bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.15,0:30:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're a bunch of\Ncutthroats who have controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this lawless area for\Nthe past 800 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.16,0:30:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they're under the\NDemon Beast's control...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll be even tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.83,0:30:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about some\Nsupport from the I MO?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got a team taking care of\Nthe Triads in Hong Kong and Macao.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.17,0:30:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to nail every last\NDemon Beast carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to face the thing\Nalone as it was being reborn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.18,0:31:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now there's two of us.\NYou and me, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.85,0:31:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.85,0:31:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell\Nyou this just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.19,0:31:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't point that nozzle\Nat Kayo or Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.20,0:31:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The minute you do,\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.54,0:31:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping the Demon Beast from\Nbeing reborn is my top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.58,0:31:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll do whatever\Nit takes to ensure that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.88,0:31:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.59,0:31:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boyfriend of yours, Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.09,0:31:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Khmer Rouge. One of the\Nbest fighters the bandits have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.23,0:31:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady in charge said\NI was to try and...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.23,0:31:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...recruit him to help\Nfight the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he could be our\Ntrickiest enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.07,0:32:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when he turned towards me,\NI saw Hoei's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.24,0:32:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there was a flash\Nof his memory of me in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.24,0:32:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.58,0:32:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe his mind and body\Nare being controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.91,0:32:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but deep in his eyes\Nwere his memories of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chuan Zui Ji...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.55,0:32:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chuan Zui Ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.63,0:32:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories Hoei and I\Nshare that can't be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.26,0:32:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to his heart\Nisn't shut completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.60,0:32:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chuan Zui Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.60,0:32:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must direct this\Npower of the heart properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.90,0:32:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and Kayo will be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.94,0:32:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.32,0:32:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, when you saved me\NI knew in my heart that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.32,0:32:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd be able to\Nsee my Hoei again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.62,0:32:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, too, was Chuan Zui Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.83,0:32:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm on my way\Nto see Hoei again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.25,0:32:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know in my heart\NI can call back to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.25,0:33:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the wonderful memory of\Nwhen we made love together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.97,0:33:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chuan Zui Ji, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.30,0:33:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.97,0:33:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to believe your love's\Nmemories aren't gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.64,0:33:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I understand, Mei Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.65,0:33:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we got company!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.06,0:33:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Stop it!\NMuneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.32,0:34:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mother...\NSource of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.74,0:34:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So glad... So delicious...\NThank you, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.05,0:34:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New lord emperor of\Nthe river... Protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.73,0:34:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Submit to me! With Mother's\Npower, I shall be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.44,0:34:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, save me!\NSave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.45,0:34:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, as long as you're with me,\Nyou've nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.75,0:34:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it anytime, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.75,0:35:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.77,0:35:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get everyone guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.18,0:35:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.85,0:36:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.48,0:36:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.15,0:36:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your back, Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.49,0:36:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.46,0:36:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.47,0:36:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.44,0:36:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.24,0:36:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.21,0:37:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Save yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.88,0:37:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.17,0:37:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.21,0:37:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your and\NHoei's Chuan Zui Ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.22,0:37:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... But, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.18,0:37:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.43,0:37:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! What are you\Ndoing to Tairunto's mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.90,0:37:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei, stop it! Stop it, Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.23,0:37:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.53,0:37:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's me, Mei Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you... Don't you\Nknow who I am? Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.33,0:37:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...? Mei Ling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.56,0:38:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MUNETO!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.53,0:38:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.28,0:38:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.29,0:38:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hold it!\N- No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.96,0:38:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei, he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.63,0:38:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He allowed me to be\Nwith you once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.97,0:38:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.97,0:38:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!\NWe're leaving together!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling, save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.65,0:38:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want you\Nto come with me! Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.94,0:38:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei... Ling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.30,0:39:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember,\Ndon't you, Hoei?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.97,0:39:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.35,0:39:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.02,0:39:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make love to me, one more time.\NLike you did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.36,0:39:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, they've become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.08,0:39:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.66,0:39:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to become\None like they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.34,0:39:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?\NThe ecstasy we felt when...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.42,0:39:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we first defeated\Nthe Demon Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.80,0:40:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It remains within us.\NThat ultimate power.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.40,0:40:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!\NI'll never let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.17,0:40:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoei!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.80,0:40:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let\Nyou go, Mei Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.72,0:40:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.77,0:40:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Why? WHY?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.35,0:42:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smoke...\NIt's them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Their souls are one,\Nreturning to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Chuan Zui Ji...\NOur using Maitreya's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.53,0:42:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of\Ntwo peoples love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.87,0:42:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to G7.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.51,0:42:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.22,0:42:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so tired...
